      "question": "Where Is My Refund?",
      "answer_paragraphs": [
        "Financial aid and other tuition credits are applied to your account after the semester starts. A Title IV form must be complete. Once all funds are posted to your account, the Student Accounting Office will begin generating refunds.",
        "In order to receive your refund, you must be enrolled in direct deposit. You may enroll through Manage My Account link in the Illinois Tech Portal."
      ],
      "full_answer": "Financial aid and other tuition credits are applied to your account after the semester starts. A Title IV form must be complete. Once all funds are posted to your account, the Student Accounting Office will begin generating refunds. In order to receive your refund, you must be enrolled in direct deposit. You may enroll through Manage My Account link in the Illinois Tech Portal.",
